{"type": "article", "id": 14597, "title": "hard graft钥匙包", "description": "", "date": "2015-09-08T06:59:34Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 30, "image": "img/article/article_show/2016060600101437XD0MHbuP8eEzkU.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t专做纯手工真皮配件的英国品牌 hard graft 近日推出了 Turn Key Pouch 钥匙包，延续了品牌的英伦质感。灰色的抽绳连着挂钥匙的金属环，不需要使用时就把线在钥匙包外缠一圈，钥匙就能收进包里了。制作上选用昂贵的植鞣革，非常耐磨，也体现了精致的做工。有深蓝色（OCEAN）和棕色（CLASSIC）两种颜色可选，售价39英镑。<a href=\"http://www.hardgraft.com/products/turn-key-ocean\" target=\"_blank\">这里是购买链接。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142045ND0wvyWZesjECuTK.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"602\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.55740741\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142045GowdHflIAmCpYMDy.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"602\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.55740741\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142047DNogGckJUwhSfrBT.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"602\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.55740741\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142047anEdBHDNtLJXKgOA.jpg\" width=\"875\" height=\"580\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66285714\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}